{"tid":469412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湖南優異生殺班主任　與兇手同班死者女兒：我不恨他，抵命沒用","createTime":"2017-11-15T09:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T09:57:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28f596a17b4450907c550a24baac3752d05b5d1a","tid":469412,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171115/s00004/75e72c1c0e35171783239750c2252a8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171115%2Fs00004%2F75e72c1c0e35171783239750c2252a8d.jpg&h=f1185650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南省16歲優異生羅Ｘ傑近日因成績反覆，班主任鮑方與他會談時要求致電其家長。羅一時激動，掏出水果刀刺死班主任。羅行兇後返回課室，向同班鮑方女兒坦白：「我把你爸爸殺了。」他其後企圖在走廊跳樓，最終被同學攔下，目前已被警方拘捕。據法醫檢查，死者被刺26刀。<br />\n<br />\n突然經歷亡父之痛，行兇者更為同學，但死者女兒受訪時表示，「我不恨他，恨不起來，一命抵一命也沒有用，希望他能改，不再傷害別人。」她指走到父親辦公室看到爸爸躺在地上，其手機在身邊已輸入醫院的電話，她遂撥通要求救援。<br />\n<br />\n死者女兒稱，行兇後羅和她說話時仍持刀，令她有些害怕，而且當時還稱要再桶其父兩刀。因當時情況混亂，她不肯定羅有沒有叫她。<br />\n<br />\n她又指父親喜歡成績好的學生，亦真的很看好羅，認為就算性格有問題也可慢慢改變。對於羅的印象，她指平日接觸不多，感覺對方平日不太想按照老師說話去做，如被批評就會很生氣地離開教室。她又形容父親是有原則的人，為人無欲無求只望教好學生。<br />\n<br />\n（澎湃新聞、南方人物周刊、北京青年報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171115/s00004/1510737869736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171115%2Fs00004%2F1510737869736&d=dr%2BBXWo2Qwm1iMWF6fO1pfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0ecf4b13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171115%2Fs00004%2F1510737869736&h=8bf54b54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171115/s00004/1510737869736</a>"},{"pid":"ae45b59241c74c6b279aad8f70377ef4facbdd8a","tid":469412,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:50:04.000Z","msg":"大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢老母呢 借黎駛下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45084eb70ab6a15b4039371aed5e826087197051","tid":469412,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1aeecae71a06842e20254ebdafdb133372a55d","tid":469412,"uid":55568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢老母呢 借黎駛下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲老母？直接借佢黎使下啦"},{"pid":"ab6d711ea5dad2de13fdf2350058271f46d7192b","tid":469412,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"有咩社會就有咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個人都要還自己有份參與既後果"},{"pid":"d9b84b6d5b7d2ff60b04cf6d0f3524970973021a","tid":469412,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢老母呢 借黎駛下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲老母？直接借佢黎使下啦</blockquote><br />\n你黎埋我個份"}]}